parameters:
\c[3]Prepare yourself if you venture into the
labyrinth known as the Abyss of Betrayal.

There is a statue of a loli monster. However, I
feel a very strong power... Would you like to
touch it?

To awaken me... is it a magical girl who has
appeared... Kikihi...
Are you perhaps the legendary loli monster...!?

A legend, how interesting. I am Orochi. I devour
all those who displease me, I am Orochi-sama.

You seem really strong. If you're interested,
would you like to fight demons with me? We could
become the ultimate fighting force.

I see, it seems that demons are still lurking
around. However, as you can see, I am currently
sealed.
If you release my seal, I will lend you my power.
How can the seal be released?

Yes, indeed. In this accursed dungeon called the
Abyss of Betrayal\C[2], there should be a magical
beast known as the Gokuhyou Daikyojin\C[0].

I want you to defeat it and bring back the Rainbow
Ice Clump. It is the source of my power. With
that, there would be no need for such sealing
rituals.

The Rainbow Ice Clump, huh? I got it...! I'll go
to the dungeon, defeat the enemies, and bring it
back.

I'm counting on you, magical girl. By the way,
what's your name?
I brought a chunk of rainbow ice!
Ohhh! The seal has been released!
I'm glad. So, you'll come with me, right?

You promised to become my ally if I released the
seal, right?

I don't knooooow! I don't know, I don't know, I
don't know, I don't know, I don't know!!! Are you
trying to give me orders, you?!

Hey, even though you're acting all cute and
magical girl-like, don't think you can
underestimate me.

I may praise you for releasing the seal, but that
alone doesn't mean I'll become your servant.

I want to go see the outside world, so goodbye for
now. Take care, Konoha! Kikihi!

What do you mean by legendary loli-mon!!!! The
promise is different, isn't it!!!!
I will definitely find you and make you my ally~
